EmailTemplate.subject: Sorry We Missed You - Resources from our Understanding the Contractor Webinar
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hello {{lead.First Name:default=Webinar Registrant}},
You were missed at MBO's webinar titled "Understanding the Contractor: 5 Challenges ICs Have with Your Enterprise" held on Thursday, August 29. Jay Lash, VP of Market Strategies at MBO Partners - Enterprise Solutions, joined two self-employed consultants to discuss the top five challenges that most ICs have doing business with Enterprise organizations. Below you will find links related to the presentation: Webinar Recording <http://video.mbopartners.com/players/v4uFa2n9-mMm4x1IW.html> Webinar Slide Deck <http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/2013-06-compliance-officer-training-webinar.ppsx> <http://sig.org/webinars.php> Connect with Jay <http://www.linkedin.com/in/jaylash> Post-Webinar Survey <http://www.surveymonkey.com/s/WJFYMPY>
